If you need to sell a house in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, we can make you a simple cash offer and buy the property as is — meaning no repairs, no cleanup, and no open houses.

This can help if you inherited a house, have tenants you do not want to manage, are behind on payments, have code violations, or just need a clean way to move on.

We handle houses across Philadelphia and the surrounding area, including brick rowhomes, brick suburban ranches and capes, and older semi-attached and borough homes that need work.

There are no commissions, no agent showings, and no pressure. If the offer works for you, you choose the closing date.

Call eight eight eight, two seven four, five zero zero six, and we will walk you through your options.
